Clark CopyInternational Corp said it acquired a majority interest inDatagraph GMBH of Lich, West Germany.    The acquisition was made through Clark Copy's majorityowned subsidiary Interactive Computer Aids of Norway.    No price was disclosed for the acquisition.    Clark Copy said worldwide sales for Datagraph, which makescolor graphics workstations, were 10 mln dlrs for the yearended Dec. 31, 1986. Reuter&#3;